text: North East High School North East High School (NEHS) is a public high school in North East, Maryland on 300 Irishtown Road. It is a part of Cecil County Public Schools. As of 2019, North East High School has 1,083 students enrolled. The school colors are blue and white. ==References== ==External links== * North East High School Category:Public high schools in Maryland Category:Schools in Cecil County, Maryland
